#define WrestleWin ["You're out of your element, %s. Let's get you to safety.","That's enough. There's no honor in fighting someone who can't defend themselves.","Take a breath, %s. The fight's over. You're not going to win this.","I didn't want it to come to this. Walk away, %s.","You have heart, but you need more training before you face me again.","You're quick, %s, but you're telegraphing every move. Keep your guard up.","Good effort, but you're not listening to the rhythm of the fight.","That's all you've got? You need to believe in your potential, %s.","You're fighting for the wrong reasons, %s. Stop and rethink your approach.","I've faced worse, and I've survived. You're not a threat to me, %s.","You’ve got grit, %s. That’s a good start for a soldier.","You forced me to use the shield, %s. Not many can say that.","Keep at it, %s. You're developing a decent tactical sense.","That was a solid strike, %s. But you're still relying too much on brute force.","You fought honorably, %s. That counts for more than winning.","Well fought, %s. You're starting to show real command on the field.","You’ve got the skills of a veteran, %s. Just don't let the ego take over.","I’m impressed, %s. You really gave me a run for my money today.","You held your ground, %s. That takes more courage than most have.","You're a strong combatant, %s. I hope to see you on the right side of this fight soon.","That was quite the scrap, %s! You have the makings of a true hero.","You've got speed and strategy, %s. It was an honor to test my mettle against you.","You’re a powerhouse, %s! Stay focused and you’ll do great things.","I haven't been challenged like that in a while, %s. You’re a formidable opponent.","You’re tough, %s, but you're fighting for the wrong cause. Let's talk.","You’re a true warrior, %s. That was a fight for the history books!","I respect your strength and your resolve, %s. You're one of the best.","That was an intense engagement, %s. You've got the skills to lead.","I'm genuinely impressed by your discipline, %s. You're a force to be reckoned with.","We fought with honor, %s. Regardless of the outcome, that’s what matters.","Holy stars, %s! That was a battle that would make even Asgardians take notice!","You’re a true legend, %s. I’m honored to have been your opponent today.","You’re elite, %s. Let’s team up and save the world together!","You pushed me to my absolute limit, %s. That’s a rare feat.","You’ve got grit, heart, and power—you’re the real deal, %s."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["I... I underestimated you, %s. A hard lesson learned.","You caught me off guard, %s. Good tactical awareness.","I’m not finished, %s. I’ll be back for the rematch.","You win this round, %s. But keep your eyes open.","That was a good strike, %s. You've got potential.","You're better than you look, %s! I'll give you that.","Nice shot, %s! I didn't see that move coming.","You've got a hidden spark, %s. Keep working on it.","I was just testing the waters, %s, but you certainly made a splash!","Okay, %s, you earned that one. Don't let it go to your head.","You're holding your own, %s! Keep pushing, and you'll go places.","You caught me slipping, %s. That's a point for you.","I like your style, soldier. You earned that win.","You're doing fine, %s. I'm going to have to work harder next time.","Not bad, %s. You're getting sharper every day.","Well hello! You're keeping me on my toes today, %s.","You looking for trouble, or are you just lucky, %s? Either way, you won today.","Stay alert, soldier. Things change in a heartbeat, and you just proved it.","You’ve got a steady hand, %s. I respect that—you bested me.","Welcome to the winner's circle, %s. Enjoy it while it lasts.","Whoa, look at you! You've got more power than I realized, %s.","I'm impressed, %s. You move like someone who’s seen a thing or two, and you just proved it.","Careful now, you're throwing around enough energy to make folks nervous, %s—and I'm one of 'em!","You’re a force to be reckoned with, %s. I'm glad you're on the right side.","Keep that energy up, %s! You're teaching me a thing or two today.","Good heavens, %s! You pack quite a punch. Where'd you learn to fight like that?","I’d be careful if I were you, %s—someone might get jealous of all that strength, but you won the day!","You’re a real powerhouse, soldier. I'm nervous to get too close now!","You’ve got grit, %s. You beat me fair and square.","Well, aren't you something else? Real pleasure to be bested by ya, %s.","My, my... you’re something truly special, ain't ya, %s?","I don't say this often, but you've got more power than most—it was an honor to lose to ya.","Welcome to the big leagues, %s. You're breaking the scenery and my record!","You’re a legend, %s. I’m honored to be standing in the same room as ya.","With that kind of strength, there ain't nothing you can't do, soldier. Just stay true to yourself."]
